data.description: Now is your chance to own this beautiful updated home in one of Okc's best locations.   3Bd, 2ba, 2Li, fireplace, and lots of room for entertaining as well as lots of storage. New paint inside and out with new carpet, tile, bathroom countertops and light fixtures.  Large backyard with storage shed and covered patio.   2-car garage with built-in work bench and storage.   Putnam City school district and great location close to Hefner parkway.  (NW 63rd and Meridian area)  This home has been well cared for and is move in ready.  (405) 620-6777
data.whatILove: Beautiful Updated and move in ready home with lots of storage in great neighborhood
